" incremental searching.
set incsearch

" Case-insensitive searching.
set ignorecase

" But case-sensitive if expression contains a capital letter.
set smartcase

" Default to global substitutions on lines
set gdefault

" Use the system pasteboard
set pasteboard

" show Assistant Editor
nmap ,t :xccmd changeToGeniusEditor<CR>
nmap ,T :xccmd removeAssistantEditor<CR>

" toggle comment
nmap ,/ :xccmd commentAndUncommentCurrentLines<CR>

" input mode
" うまくいかないのでXCodeのキーバインドで設定
" imap <C-H> <Left>
" imap <C-L> <Right>
" imap <C-D> <Del>

